      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, suggesting major repairs are likely needed soon. The exterior has extensive paint fading, several large dents, and some rust spots, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is recommended for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts, as it is not currently reliable for daily transportation.",
