    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home and someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to life. While it currently shows significant wear and will require substantial repairs and attention, it presents a great opportunity for a budget-friendly project or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge at a great price, this is the one for you!",
