    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This model has been meticulously maintained, exhibiting a level of care that ensures both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. The interior remains refined and well-preserved, while the exterior maintains a professional finish. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for a discerning driver to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances performance with sophisticated value. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
